<apex:page renderAs="pdf" controller="ProgramEnrollmentInvoiceController">
    <html>
        <head>
            <style>
                body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; }
                h1 { font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
                table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; }
                th, td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 6px; text-align: left; }
                th { background-color: #f2f2f2; }
                a { color: blue; text-decoration: underline; }
            </style>
        </head>
        <body>
            <h1>Invoice - {!ProgramEnrollment.Name}</h1>
            <p>
                <b>Student:</b> {!ProgramEnrollment.hed__Contact__r.Name}<br/>
                <b>Program:</b> {!ProgramEnrollment.Program__c}<br/>
                <b>Enrollment Status:</b> {!ProgramEnrollment.Enrollment_Status__c}<br/>
                <b>Date:</b> {!TODAY()}
            </p>

            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Course Connection ID</th>
                    <th>Course Name</th>
                    <th>Term</th>
                    <th>Course Start</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                    <th>Course Fee</th>
                </tr>
                <apex:repeat value="{!CourseConnections}" var="cc">
                    <tr>
                        <td>{!cc.Name}</td>
                        <td>{!cc.Course__r.Name}</td>
                        <td>{!cc.Term__c}</td>
                        <td>{!cc.Start_Date__c}</td>
                        <td>{!cc.Status__c}</td>
                        <td>${!TEXT(cc.Course_Fee__c,"#,###.00")}</td>
                    </tr>
                </apex:repeat>
            </table>

            <p style="margin-top:15px;">
                Enrollment is confirmed once payment is received. Courses may be paid for in advance or on a term-by-term basis. 
                Courses paid in advance will not be subject to future enrollment fee increases. Courses fill on a first-come, 
                first-served basis and many courses tend to fill ahead of the registration deadline.
            </p>

            <p><b>Enrollment deadlines:</b><br/>
                Fall: Aug 1 &nbsp;&nbsp; Winter: Dec 1 &nbsp;&nbsp; Spring: Mar 1
            </p>

            <p><b>Accepted forms of Payment:</b></p>
            <ul>
                <li>For UCSF fund payments, send chartstring/speedtype to <a href="mailto:ImplementationScience@ucsf.edu">ImplementationScience@ucsf.edu</a>.</li>
                <li>Credit Card (Visa/MasterCard): 
                    <a href="https://secure.payconex.net/paymentpage/enhanced/index.php?action=view&aid=120615635381&id=140324">
                        Payment Portal
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>Electronic Wire: email confirmation with learner + course to 
                    <a href="mailto:Online-Education@ucsf.edu">Online-Education@ucsf.edu</a> and 
                    <a href="mailto:ImplementationScience@ucsf.edu">ImplementationScience@ucsf.edu</a>.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <p><b>Bank Information:</b><br/>
                Bank of America<br/>
                2000 Clayton Road<br/>
                Concord, CA 94520<br/>
                ABA Routing (Wire): 026009593<br/>
                SWIFT (International Wires): BOFAUS3N<br/>
                ACH Routing: 121000358
            </p>
        </body>
    </html>
</apex:page>